    public final class Collapse<_1,_2>
extends Object
implements BiMonoidFactory<Monoid<_1>,Monoid<_2>,Tuple2<_1,_2>>
    A Monoid instance formed by a Tuple2<_1, _2> and monoids over _1 and _2. Successively collapses multiple Tuple2s into a single Tuple2 by collapsing the values of each slot under the provided monoid instance.

    For the Semigroup, see Collapse.
